name: Power Station
desc: The basic structure of the territory expansion. It must be connected to the territory to take effect. It needs to be built with amethyst. Amethyst can be obtained by gathering in the Alliance territory or special resource area

name: Alliance Fortress
desc: You need to build an Alliance fortress before having territory. When there is only one Alliance fortress; the fortress cannot be demolished actively. Amethyst is required for construction. Amethyst can be obtained by gathering in the Alliance territory or special resource area

name: Expedition Outpost
desc: The Outpost outside the Eternal Land. Conquer the outpost to increase Alliance and Warzone honor faster. The outposts are guarded by the Dark Legion. You may earn rewards by defeating the guards for the first time.
